@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
@studentId = YOUR_STUDENT_ID_HERE
@installmentId = YOUR_INSTALLMENT_ID_HERE

### ============================================
### PAYMENT REMINDERS
### ============================================

### 1. Test payment reminder scheduler
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/test-scheduler
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2. Send manual payment reminder to specific installment
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/payment-reminder/{{installmentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### ATTENDANCE WARNINGS
### ============================================

### 3. Get all at-risk students (attendance < 75%)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/at-risk-students
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 4. Send manual attendance warning to specific student
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/attendance-warning/{{studentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### HOW TO USE THIS FILE
### ============================================
# 
# Step 1: Get your admin token
#   - Login as admin using auth.http
#   - Copy the token from the response
#   - Replace YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE above
#
# Step 2: Get student/installment IDs
#   - Use students.http or payments.http to get IDs
#   - Replace YOUR_STUDENT_ID_HERE and YOUR_INSTALLMENT_ID_HERE
#
# Step 3: Click "Send Request" above any endpoint
#
### ============================================